column2: b'Tales of Symphonia The Animation: Kratos-sensei no Private Lesson'

b'A special bonus animation included in the first volume of the Tales of Symphonia DVD.\nLloyd and Collete talk about the special DVD editions, and Professor Kratos gives a summary of the ancient history of the world in Tales of Symphonia.'
[b'Tales of Symphonia The Animation: Sylvarant-hen', b'Tales of Symphonia The Animation: Kaette Kita Kratos-sensei no Private Lesson']
